{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01SDAPGgSDUhPEp6fyxX2AYH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration is complete. Here is the full report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Spring Boot 3.1.0 → Quarkus 3.8.4\n\n**High-level actions:**\n1. Flattened multi-module project (roster-common + roster-boot) into single-module\n2. Replaced all Spring dependencies with Quarkus equivalents\n3. Migrated REST controller from Spring MVC annotations to JAX-RS\n4. Migrated service layer from `@Service` to CDI `@ApplicationScoped`\n5. Kept Spring Data JPA repos via `quarkus-spring-data-jpa` compatibility layer, added explicit `@Query` JPQL\n6. Migrated configuration from Spring properties to Quarkus properties\n7. Migrated integration tests from `@SpringBootTest` to `@QuarkusTest`\n8. Updated Dockerfile CMD from `spring-boot:run` to Quarkus uber-jar execution\n9. Created comprehensive smoke tests\n\n**Overall outcome:** SUCCESS - all smoke tests pass (6/6 external, 55/55 internal)\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Single-module Quarkus project (was multi-module Spring Boot)\n- Dockerfile: Updated CMD for Quarkus jar execution\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Quarkus configuration\n- src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/rest/RosterController.java: Spring MVC → JAX-RS\n- src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java: @Service → @ApplicationScoped\n- src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java: SpringBootApplication → JAX-RS Application\n- src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/repository/PlayerRepository.java: Added @Query JPQL\n- src/test/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RequestCrudIT.java: @SpringBootTest → @QuarkusTest\n- src/test/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RequestQueriesIT.java: @SpringBootTest → @QuarkusTest\n\nAdded:\n- smoke.py: Comprehensive REST API smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-boot/ (entire directory - Spring Boot module)\n- roster-common/ (entire directory - common module)\n- .mvn/ (Maven wrapper directory)\n- src/test/java/.../RequestSmokeText,java (misnamed file with comma)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 1 warning resolved during migration\n- **Warning - removeTeam session cache:** After `removeTeam`, the `getTeamsOfLeague` query returned the deleted team due to Hibernate's first-level cache not being properly synced with the bidirectional `@OneToMany` relationship. Fixed by explicitly removing the team from the league's collection before deletion.\n- **No critical issues.** Migration completed fully."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":516,"cache_read_input_tokens":130639,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":516,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":693},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d54aa1ac-75bb-4334-9153-448f533619ac","uuid":"f4c9bf5d-3977-47ca-8cba-12487fae8e45"}
